{"tid":2008070,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"九龍東同港島都有特訓Channel啦","createTime":"2020-05-08T17:59:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T16:00:54.000Z","uid":200786,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ecc49a3bfe6d56ca2641ed0a953fb7f76c993093","tid":2008070,"uid":200786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T17:59:19.000Z","msg":"頭先開錯台，再開過<br />\n<br />\n九龍東<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F8FoBHi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF8FoBHi.jpg&h=9d6c8b21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/txu1oni.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftxu1oni.jpg&h=686efb0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n#推廣時間<br />\n<br />\n各位學員們，希望大家可以幫下手推廣吓我哋呢個channel 除咗叫你哋身邊嘅朋友一齊操之外仲可以將我哋既文宣印出嚟畀你哋附近嘅黃店貼出嚟等多啲人一齊操fit 自己<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n從來都唔係一個口號而係一個行動<br />\n<br />\nTg link:<a href=\"https://t.me/ekrtc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fekrtc&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7d2VlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=949d272b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/ekrtc</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n港島<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QAFsiVK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQAFsiVK.jpg&h=6f723902&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n歡迎各位學員加入港島特訓<br />\n本頻道星期一(20/4) 21:00 開始將會進行首課家中訓練 <br />\n特訓前希望請將港島特訓分享比身邊既朋友<br />\n<br />\n鍛鍊體格 積極備戰 係抗爭者必須擁有嘅態度<br />\n讓革命融入生活 以行動光復香港<br />\n_________<br />\n港島特訓HKITC：<br />\n@HKisland_Training<br />\n港島特訓助理 ：<br />\n@HKisland_training_bot<br />\n<br />\nTg link: <a href=\"https://t.me/HKisland_training\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKisland_training&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7d2VlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=9aab6e2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKisland_training</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9803ac11a02d9f5ddafdb8e5c4b7133fcb273d23","tid":2008070,"uid":200786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T17:59:33.000Z","msg":"十連推"},{"pid":"db78fa3cac29324f6ff679ac84874ccf51b7c378","tid":2008070,"uid":200786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T17:59:46.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"faa28a21e5de2154bcad4443a6d319d60383a023","tid":2008070,"uid":200786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T17:59:59.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"9c0b4f7c9590d57fd4ad169000f552b97afeab94","tid":2008070,"uid":200786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T